sentences: Anders Nielsen (born 4 March 1974), known professionally as Anders Kjølholm, is a Danish bassist, best known as the former bassist of the Danish heavy metal band Volbeat.
In November 2015 the band announced that Kjølholm would leave Volbeat.
Poulsen and Larsen said that "Anders has been a loyal friend and bandmate since 2001.
In 2020 he became a member of the hard rock band Ace it Moe.
We’re very thankful for this and wish Anders all the best in the future."
